<view class="page"><view class="nav" style="padding-top:{{navTop}}px;height:{{navHeight}}px"><view bindtap="goBack"><image src="{{icons.back}}"/><text>返回学员详情</text></view></view><scroll-view class="scroll" scroll-y enhanced show-scrollbar="{{false}}"><view style="height:{{navSpacer}}px"></view><view class="content">
<text class="title">学员课包与课消</text><text class="subtitle">学员课包详情与课消记录</text>
<view class="profile"><image src="{{avatar}}" mode="aspectFill"/><view><view class="name"><text>刘承宇</text><text>♂</text><text>10岁</text></view><text>星火校区 · 启航班</text><view class="state"><view></view><text>在读</text></view></view><view class="ball"></view></view>
<view class="package"><view class="package-head"><image src="{{icons.calendar}}"/><text>U10进阶课</text><text>当前课包</text></view><view class="numbers"><view><text>已使用</text><view><text>24</text><text>课时</text></view></view><view><text>总课时</text><view><text>30</text><text>课时</text></view></view><view><text>剩余课时</text><view class="orange"><text>6</text><text>课时</text></view></view></view><view class="progress"><view></view></view><view class="progress-copy">使用进度 <text>80%</text></view><view class="expiry"><image src="{{icons.calendar}}"/><text>有效期至</text><text>2025-06-30</text><text>（剩余 <text>18</text> 天）</text></view></view>
<view class="renewal"><view class="bell">♢</view><view><text>续费提醒</text><text>课包即将到期，建议尽快跟进续费</text></view><text>18 天后到期</text></view>
<view class="section-head"><view><image src="{{icons.clock}}"/><text>最近课消记录</text></view><text>最近4条</text></view><view class="record-list"><view class="record" wx:for="{{records}}" wx:key="id" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="openRecord"><image src="{{icons.calendar}}"/><view><text>{{item.date}}　{{item.time}}</text><text>{{item.className}}</text></view><view><text>{{item.lesson}}</text><text>{{item.type}}</text></view></view></view>
<view class="tip"><image src="{{icons.warning}}"/><view><text>小贴士</text><text>本课包剩余课时较少，建议及时跟进续费，避免影响上课安排。</text></view></view><view class="actions"><button bindtap="openAll">查看全部记录</button><button bindtap="createRenewal">＋　创建续费跟进</button></view><view class="safe"></view></view></scroll-view></view>
